cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the calibration of a car-following model using trajectory data, which involves optimization and numerical methods. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Among these, cs.SY is the most likely category since the paper deals with control systems and optimization. The other categories are also relevant since the paper involves machine learning, numerical methods, and network analysis.
